item.title: GM
item.description: score:244 Chances: General Motors (GM) delivered strong results in 2023, with a 14% increase in vehicle deliveries in the United States due to improvements in the supply chain and increased incentives. Wolfe Research analyst Rod Lache upgraded shares of General Motors to Buy from Hold, citing positive trends and set a $42 price target.
